20:52.399 --> 20:53.220
God says, you know what?

20:53.440 --> 20:54.261
I have the authority.

20:55.002 --> 20:56.584
I'm over your life.

20:57.505 --> 21:02.371
But as you trust me with that, whatever you put under God's authority, he blesses.

21:03.553 --> 21:04.754
What a cool thought, right?

21:05.154 --> 21:07.197
Okay, God, you're calling me to step out of faith.

21:07.518 --> 21:08.980
So God's putting a number in your heart.

21:09.220 --> 21:12.185
