22:25.295 --> 22:27.218
He's saying this really starts in

22:27.426 --> 22:28.447
in Jerusalem.

22:28.467 --> 22:29.328
It's in three areas.

22:29.348 --> 22:30.229
Jerusalem, where's that?

22:30.349 --> 22:31.590
That's Springfield and Joplin.

22:31.610 --> 22:32.731
That's James of a church.

22:32.771 --> 22:37.616
That's us building what God is doing, where he's planted us, where he's called us.

22:37.676 --> 22:40.899
