22:40.959 --> 22:42.861
That's like Southwest Missouri is Judea.

22:42.881 --> 22:44.362
And then Samaria is like the US.

22:44.382 --> 22:51.009
And that's why we're planting 22 churches across the US because we feel called to reach our Samaria.

22:52.650 --> 22:54.152
And then to the ends of the earth.

22:54.192 --> 22:56.754
And historically, as a church, we've been

22:56.898 --> 22:58.961
So, God has really blessed us.

22:59.041 --> 23:07.636
