23:53.029 --> 23:55.071
We're going to be planting churches in Indonesia.

23:55.291 --> 23:57.554
We're going to be planting churches in Ethiopia.

23:57.814 --> 23:59.316
Come on, can we praise the Lord for that?

23:59.456 --> 24:00.057
I love that.

24:02.940 --> 24:10.790
Let me talk to you just briefly about France because France is one of the most secular nations in the world.

24:12.512 --> 24:14.514
In fact, since 2022,

24:15.170 --> 24:19.818
Violent crime against Christians has dramatically increased.

24:20.198 --> 24:28.252
It's on a rate that is nearly 50% up since 2022 with 900 incidents that are on track to happen.

24:28.652 --> 24:30.996
Only 8% of people attend church in France.

24:31.016 --> 24:34.021
8%.

24:34.201 --> 24:39.951
And God's calling us to say, you know what?

24:40.612 --> 24:41.874
We're going to reach a nation.

24:42.466 --> 24:44.609
We're gonna plant four churches in France.

24:44.890 --> 24:46.452
We're gonna be planting in one in Paris.

24:46.472 --> 24:47.474
How awesome is that?

24:48.095 --> 24:49.236
Yeah, let's praise the Lord for that.

24:51.500 --> 24:54.985
Corsica, play bond, Rin.

24:55.827 --> 25:02.477
Paris, the church we're planting is gonna be called House of Miracles, putting a stake in the ground for Jesus in Paris.

25:02.537 --> 25:03.178
How awesome.

25:05.822 --> 25:10.930
Corsica, there's one church in Corsica, only one church for every 350,000 people.

25:12.322 --> 25:16.728
In Ren, it's 0.2% Christian.

25:18.290 --> 25:19.872
It's a university city.

25:20.613 --> 25:27.702
And the church we're planting there, they believe they're going to be able to plant a new church every three years out of the church we're planting in Ren.

25:27.942 --> 25:32.087
God is going to use us to change the nation of France in Jesus' name.

25:32.127 --> 25:32.828
Praise the Lord.

25:32.868 --> 25:36.153
We're going to be planting churches in Thailand.

25:36.854 --> 25:40.338
And Thailand is 94% Buddhist.

25:40.546 --> 25:54.736
You're going to hear that a similar percentage in the places we're going because we believe God has called us to transform dark places.

25:56.460 --> 25:57.362
Sometimes we can

25:57.666 --> 26:00.389
Get the sense that everything's being done that needs to be done.

26:00.449 --> 26:00.950
