26:01.150 --> 26:03.593
There are nations that need to be changed for Jesus.

26:03.894 --> 26:06.557
And God is calling us as a church to be a part of it.

26:06.777 --> 26:08.059
And Thailand is going to be changed.

26:08.079 --> 26:10.441
We're going to be planting four churches in Thailand.

26:10.461 --> 26:11.022
I'll show you.

26:11.042 --> 26:12.344
One of those is in Bangkok.

26:12.364 --> 26:18.711
We're putting a church in the heart of Thailand in the capital city to say, Thailand is for Jesus.

26:18.731 --> 26:20.794
94%, no more.

26:21.074 --> 26:22.676
Christianity is moving forward.

26:22.917 --> 26:27.442
The heart of God is going to be birthed in Thailand through what we're doing.

26:27.554 --> 26:29.876
It's gonna be powerful, I love that.

26:30.317 --> 26:32.079
We're gonna be planting churches in Indonesia.

26:33.100 --> 26:47.435
And these dots actually on this Indonesian map are just placeholder dots, not because we don't know where the churches are gonna be planted, but because we can't announce them publicly because the church is so persecuted in Indonesia.

26:48.856 --> 26:54.482
It's the largest Muslim country with 240 million Muslims.

26:56.226 --> 27:05.401
And we're gonna be planting two churches, believing God is gonna change the nation of Indonesia in a powerful way.

27:07.424 --> 27:18.982
Places, cities that have no gospel witness are gonna have a gospel witness because of what James River Church has been called to do because people stepped out in faith in a powerful way in Indonesia.

27:19.764 --> 27:21.446
God is gonna change that country.

27:22.748 --> 27:23.730
In Ethiopia,

27:24.514 --> 27:29.541
We're gonna be planting five churches and drilling water wells right next to them.

27:31.104 --> 27:31.644
I love that.

27:32.546 --> 27:33.847
Do you know why that's so powerful?

27:34.929 --> 27:40.217
Waterborne illness is absolutely ravaging places in Africa.

27:40.237 --> 27:48.008
70,000 kids die of waterborne illness every single year in the continent of Africa.

27:48.028 --> 27:52.274
70,000 kids die.

28:06.338 --> 28:15.930
But when we say, God, we may not be able to put wells everywhere in Africa right now, but we're gonna do what you've called us to do.

28:16.210 --> 28:18.453
We're gonna do what we can by faith.

28:19.855 --> 28:25.362
Jesus said, if you give a cup of cold water to one of the least of these in my name, it's as though you've done it for me.

28:28.506 --> 28:29.066
And you know what?

28:29.086 --> 28:35.154
Thousands and thousands of kids are gonna have healthy,

28:35.586 --> 28:43.059
clean water because of what we're going to do in Ethiopia, and it's going to open up doors for the gospel in a powerful way.

28:45.263 --> 28:53.338
One of the ways we know this is so effective is we had the opportunity as the church to do a similar project in Kenya.

28:53.638 --> 28:57.606
I actually had the opportunity to go to a village when we dedicated a water well.

28:58.187 --> 29:00.050
To see the excitement

29:00.482 --> 29:11.077
But to also hear the stories of how it opens up doors for the gospel, how Muslim clerics will come and they'll be a part of the dedication and it's an opportunity, they're being reached through what we're doing.

29:11.658 --> 29:18.187
Towns where there's not an openness to the gospel, we're able to build a church because we did it with water.

29:18.348 --> 29:20.931
And so I don't want to just tell you about it, I want to show you.

29:21.232 --> 29:22.834
So check out the screens right now.

29:24.194 --> 29:29.081
The challenge with Kenya and most of the East African countries, it's all desert.

29:29.281 --> 29:36.471
Very, very dry areas and the communities in those areas definitely have to walk long distances in such a water.

29:36.611 --> 29:42.540
We had projects funded by James River, they were wells and also places of worship.

29:42.680 --> 29:47.186
They have been able to share the possible of the Lord Jesus Christ.

29:47.298 --> 29:51.463
What James River Church did is very, very transformative.

29:51.483 --> 29:56.569
We have about 15,000 people that are receiving water or receiving the gospel.

29:56.609 --> 29:58.532
We have very, very clean water now.

29:58.692 --> 30:06.401
To sincerely thank James River for giving resources that have gone into building this water project.

30:06.421 --> 30:16.914
It's a seed that has been planted in the lives of our people and a seed that will germinate, produce and grow to have a huge harvest.

30:18.114 --> 30:19.416
Awesome, I love that.

30:22.840 --> 30:23.541
So exciting.

30:23.581 --> 30:31.752
And there's more to do in Ethiopia, 60% of people in Ethiopia don't have access to clean water.

30:32.072 --> 30:35.136
So we're going to bring change to that, put up the map of Ethiopia.

30:35.357 --> 30:41.364
These are the places where we're going to be planting churches and drilling water wells, which is powerful and exciting.

30:41.665 --> 30:42.546
I'll tell you this.

30:42.786 --> 30:47.850
Another great aspect of what we're doing is the church there then maintains the well.

30:48.171 --> 30:59.821
So the well lasts for years to come because they're able to be a part of it, maintaining it, and I'm telling you this is gonna make a difference, not just in these locations, but in the entire nation.

30:59.981 --> 31:02.563
God is gonna use it to reach people for Jesus.

31:02.623 --> 31:08.248
God is gonna use it to touch people who are walking, who are in darkness, and need the light of Jesus Christ.

31:08.568 --> 31:12.772
And we're saying, God, we wanna be the hands and feet of Jesus, and we wanna share

31:12.752 --> 31:14.154
heart of the gospel.

31:14.535 --> 31:17.820
And so this Ethiopia project, it costs $350,000.

31:18.661 --> 31:21.425
So maybe you would say, you know what?

31:22.026 --> 31:25.932
I feel like God has blessed me and I want to be a part of reaching that country.

31:25.952 --> 31:27.955
I want to adopt the whole country of Ethiopia.

31:27.975 --> 31:28.997
Maybe you could do that.

31:29.297 --> 31:31.861
And I'm telling you, what a powerful statement.

31:32.101 --> 31:35.206
What a powerful act of faith that God will use you.

31:35.266 --> 31:36.488
Or maybe you say, you know what?

31:36.528 --> 31:40.434
We want to do a well in a church that's $70,000.

31:41.410 --> 31:43.195
If God's putting in your heart, do it.

31:44.318 --> 31:46.404
Step out in faith, watch what God will do.

31:46.424 --> 31:52.281
Or maybe you want to be a part of one of the church plants that we talked about in France and Indonesia and Thailand.

31:53.003 --> 31:56.914
Each one of those church plants costs $25,000.

31:57.794 --> 32:00.318
So you could adopt the whole country of France for $100,000.

32:00.438 --> 32:12.175
You could say, you know what, I believe God's touching me to change France, and I'm gonna adopt that whole nation, or maybe you say, you know what, I wanna plant a church in Indonesia, and we're gonna give you $25,000.

32:12.556 --> 32:16.542
What God is speaking to you, that's when you step out in faith.

32:17.483 --> 32:26.036
We tell you about the projects, because this is what we believe God is calling us to do as a church, but it says people say, you know what, I wanna be a part of what God is doing.

32:26.336 --> 32:27.698
I wanna step out in faith.

32:27.842 --> 32:38.377
That's when faith, combined with people taking the step of faith and giving, that's where where it's like, man, God just goes, okay, breathe on it, blesses it.

32:38.998 --> 32:44.906
And we're able to do more than we ever thought was possible because as a church, we say, God, we're ready.

32:45.367 --> 32:46.108
We want that.

32:46.409 --> 32:47.610
We're, send us.

32:49.112 --> 32:53.118
I love what we're gonna be doing through Bible translation, through the seed company.

32:54.060 --> 32:55.762
It's gonna be powerful.

32:56.258 --> 32:58.120
I just want you to think about this for a second.

32:59.062 --> 33:04.989
In English, there are over 900 translations of the Bible.

33:07.031 --> 33:18.145
Yet there are 550 languages that don't have a single part of the word of God in their language.

33:18.165 --> 33:19.087
Not a single part.

33:19.627 --> 33:20.408
We have over 900.

33:22.591 --> 33:25.074
So we felt called

33:25.538 --> 33:27.420
to say, God, we want to change that.

33:28.902 --> 33:34.007
We're going to be translating the Bible for over 200 million people.

33:34.067 --> 33:35.548
Put up the map where we're going to be doing that.

33:36.670 --> 33:37.531
Here's how this works.

33:37.671 --> 33:45.159
When we do Bible translation, we have to give you sections so we can't tell you specifically where these are.

33:45.199 --> 33:50.604
Much like Indonesia, we're not able to tell you because of the persecution over Bible translation.

33:50.644 --> 33:52.306
Literally, they'll go in and stop it.

33:54.082 --> 33:55.624
But we're going to be translating the Bible.

33:55.944 --> 33:59.649
Some of these places, we're transcending Matthew, Mark, Luke, and John.

33:59.689 --> 34:02.893
Some of the places were able to translate nine books of the New Testament.

34:02.953 --> 34:06.077
Some places were able to translate six books of the New Testament.

34:06.317 --> 34:10.342
But we're saying, God, we're bringing your word to the nations.

34:10.442 --> 34:14.206
Because how many of you know people are changed by the word of God?

34:14.267 --> 34:16.710
People are transformed by the word of God.

34:16.730 --> 34:19.433
As we bring His word to them, lives are going to change.

34:19.493 --> 34:21.696
It's going to spread like wildfire.

34:22.016 --> 34:23.698
And we get to be

34:23.874 --> 34:25.076
a part of it.

34:25.396 --> 34:28.120
The entire Bible translation project costs $250,000.

34:28.200 --> 34:39.996
I believe God's touching people's heart right now to say, I want to do that.

34:41.698 --> 34:44.683
I want to bring Bible translation to the nations.

34:45.924 --> 34:50.130
And you know, when we bring the Bible translation to the nations, we're speeding the return of Christ.

34:50.754 --> 34:54.518
Jesus said the gospel where we preach the whole world and then the end will come.

34:54.878 --> 35:02.225
We're speeding Jesus' return when we bring the word of God to the nations and that's a powerful, powerful thought.

35:03.726 --> 35:05.067
Jesus' heart is for the lost.

35:07.350 --> 35:10.332
And we're called to have a heart for what his heart is for.

35:11.233 --> 35:12.134
We're called to go.

35:14.416 --> 35:16.118
Go and make disciples Jesus said.

35:18.280 --> 35:20.562
But maybe you're thinking, well, how can I go?

35:21.794 --> 35:23.376
How can I go, Brandon?

35:23.396 --> 35:23.876
I live here.

35:24.417 --> 35:29.722
Some people listening, you're called to go by actually going out on the mission field.

35:29.742 --> 35:30.463
God's putting your heart.

35:30.483 --> 35:31.644
Maybe he's calling you today.

35:31.964 --> 35:36.569
But for most of us, we're called to go by sending.

35:37.910 --> 35:38.911
Paul said it like this.

35:38.971 --> 35:42.975
He said, how can they believe in him if they've never heard about him?

35:43.255 --> 35:45.638
And how can they hear about him unless somebody tells them?

35:45.858 --> 35:50.002
And how can anyone go and tell them without being sent?

35:51.458 --> 35:53.560
For some people, they go physically.

35:53.820 --> 36:01.828
For most of us, we go by sending, by being a missionary of supply, saying, God, I'm gonna be a missionary.

36:01.989 --> 36:03.250
I'm gonna go by sending.

36:03.430 --> 36:08.695
I'm gonna fill out a card, and God, I'm gonna fill this out, and I'm gonna be a missionary of supply.

36:08.976 --> 36:11.799
I'm gonna be sending people to translate the word of God.

36:12.379 --> 36:14.021
You and I aren't in Ethiopia.

36:15.743 --> 36:19.186
We're not in the Pacific, translating the Bible.

36:19.618 --> 36:24.325
But we can be there and go there as a missionary of supply.

36:25.587 --> 36:26.969
What a powerful thought.

36:28.571 --> 36:30.855
You could say, God, I want to be a missionary of supply.

36:30.895 --> 36:32.157
You write a number by faith.

36:32.377 --> 36:37.625
You start giving and you watch what God would use you to do to change a nation.

36:38.266 --> 36:39.347
We go by sending.

36:39.387 --> 36:40.970
And here's the exciting thing.

36:41.430 --> 36:43.974
As we go, Jesus' power will go with us.

36:44.895 --> 36:49.362
He says, and behold, I am with you always, even to the end,

36:49.538 --> 36:50.319
of the age.

36:51.361 --> 36:53.646
There's something we can be absolutely certain of.

36:53.946 --> 36:55.349
Life can have questions.

36:55.389 --> 36:58.414
It's like, well, I want to do this this year.

36:58.434 --> 36:59.637
I don't know how that's going to turn out.

36:59.657 --> 37:01.500
But here's the thing we can be absolutely certain of.

37:01.841 --> 37:03.984
When we say God, we're going to take a step of faith.

37:04.525 --> 37:05.527
God, we're going to step out.

37:05.748 --> 37:07.010
And we're going to be a part of what you're doing.

37:07.250 --> 37:11.378
We can be absolutely certain his power will go with you.

37:12.930 --> 37:14.372
How will this happen, God?

37:14.592 --> 37:17.716
Are you putting a number in my heart that I'm not sure how I could do it?

37:17.956 --> 37:20.900
God says, well, I know you can't do it, but I know this.

37:21.020 --> 37:24.685
As you step out on faith, you can be certain I will be with you.

37:24.965 --> 37:26.307
My power is going to go with you.

37:26.487 --> 37:37.100
You're going to see me do things through you that you never imagined were possible because my power will go with you as you step out in faith.

37:39.483 --> 37:42.066
As you're a missionary supply, Beth and I, we've seen that.

37:43.362 --> 37:44.083
in our lives.

37:47.286 --> 37:48.848
Honestly, started with my parents.

37:52.772 --> 37:59.779
I remember having conversations with my dad about moments like this where they were making a faith promise.

38:01.421 --> 38:10.610
And him saying, you know, I was gonna do this, but after I prayed about it, I really felt like we needed to go bigger.

38:12.930 --> 38:20.858
And then he would talk to us about the blessing they'd seen in their lives because they stepped out in faith.

38:22.460 --> 38:26.684
And I mention that because Beth and I, we listen.

38:26.804 --> 38:29.467
We ask the Lord, the Lord speak to us.

38:29.787 --> 38:30.968
We put seed in the ground.

38:31.008 --> 38:34.092
We say, God use us because we believe we've seen it.

38:34.132 --> 38:36.074
Now we're seeing it in our own lives.

38:37.435 --> 38:40.498
And we have our own stories to tell our kids now

38:40.706 --> 38:47.778
of how God came through, of how God used us, and we see them stepping out in faith, saying, oh, God, would you use me?

38:47.818 --> 38:51.944
That's the power of what's happening today.

38:52.245 --> 38:59.356
A faith step bursts other faith steps, not just in our own lives, but in the lives of people around us, in our kids' lives.

38:59.537 --> 39:02.802
As we say, God, we want to live a life of faith.

39:03.842 --> 39:06.827
It impacts the people around us and it's powerful.

39:07.068 --> 39:07.649
Here's the truth.

39:07.929 --> 39:15.102
Proverbs says it like this, if people can't see what God is doing, they stumble all over themselves, but when they attend to what he's revealed, they're blessed.

39:16.745 --> 39:19.690
When you say, God, I want to, I sent your presence on this.

39:19.750 --> 39:20.993
I want to be a part of what you're doing.

